OL,3,C'A landmark moment' - Bristol first UK
OL,4,Ccity to get regular drug checking
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FThe UK's first regular drug-checking
OL,8,Fservice will begin in Bristol this
OL,9,Fmonth.
OL,11,FIt is set to open its doors for the
OL,12,Ffirst time on 27 January and will run
OL,13,Fonce a month, with additional testing
OL,14,Fdates to be announced during the year
OL,15,Fahead.
OL,17,FThe service is being delivered by harm
OL,18,Freduction charity The Loop and is
OL,19,Ffunded by Bristol City Council.
