OL,3,C'A landmark moment' - Bristol first UK
OL,4,Ccity to get regular drug checking
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FThe Loop Bristol Drug Checking Service
OL,8,Faims to signpost people using drugs to
OL,9,Fsupport services and to help save
OL,10,Flives by preventing the risk of
OL,11,Fpoisoning and overdose.
OL,13,FThe amnesty bin drop-off and Loop
OL,14,Fmobile laboratory are located at
OL,15,FBristol DrugJProject (BDP) in
OL,16,FBrunswick Square, St Paul's.
OL,18,FThe consultations will take place at a
OL,19,Flocal community centre once a month
OL,20,Ffor a year on the last weekend of the
OL,21,Fmonth.
