OL,3,C'A landmark moment' - Bristol first UK
OL,4,Ccity to get regular drug checking
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FHow will it work?
OL,9,FPeople who use the service can take
OL,10,Fsubstances of concern to BDP,
OL,11,Fsurrender a small amount into an
OL,12,Famnesty box on the ground floor, and
OL,13,Fthen an hour later return to the
OL,14,Fcommunity centre where they will
OL,15,Freceive a consultation.
OL,17,FA mobile lab will analyse the
OL,18,Fsubmitted substance using several
OL,19,Fchemical tests to identify the
OL,20,Fcontents and strength.
