OL,4,Ccity to get regular drug checking
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FThe laboratory has a Home Office
OL,8,Flicence to handle controlled drugs and
OL,9,Fthe conditions of the licence allow
OL,10,Findividual test results to be
OL,11,Fdisseminated directly to service users
OL,12,Fwho are over 18 years old and
OL,13,Fconsidered to be dependent users.
OL,15,FNo drugs are handed back to users of
OL,16,Fthe service.
