OL,4,Ccity to get regular drug checking
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FProfessor Fiona Measham, Founder and
OL,8,FChair of Trustees of The Loop and
OL,9,FChair inJCriminology at the University
OL,10,Fof Liverpool, said: "This is a
OL,11,Flandmark moment for harm reduction.
OL,13,F"After 12 years of preparations,
OL,14,Fevaluations and negotiations, it is
OL,15,Ffantastic news that The Loop can start
OL,16,Fthe UK's first regular drug-checking
OL,17,Fservice.
