OL,3,C'A landmark moment' - Bristol first UK
OL,4,Ccity to get regular drug checking
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,F"With more cities due to follow soon,
OL,8,Fthis launch represents the start of a
OL,9,Fnew era forJdrug checking and it could
OL,10,Fnot come at a more important time. The
OL,11,Frisks from adulteration of the illegal
OL,12,Fdrug market have never been greater."
OL,14,FThe new drug testing service aligns
OL,15,Fwith the aspirations set out in the
OL,16,FBristol Drug and Alcohol strategy.
