OL,4,Ccity to get regular drug checking
OL,5,Cservice
OL,7,FCouncillor Ellie King, Cabinet Lead
OL,8,Ffor Public Health and Communities,
OL,9,Fsaid: "I am proud that Bristol is the
OL,10,Ffirst city in the UK to have a regular
OL,11,Fdrug checking service. This new
OL,12,Finitiative is ultimately going to save
OL,13,Flives.
OL,15,F"It also means our communities will be
OL,16,Fable to access scientific and evidence-
OL,17,Fbased information about the drugs that
OL,18,Fthey may consume and that are in
OL,19,Fcirculation.
